articles.title: "Thomas Tuchel Adalah Diktator Sesungguhnya!" - Para Pemain Chelsea Diingatkan Soal Watak Sang Manajer - Goal.com
articles.description: Manchester United's defeat to Sheffield United had been "in the post", according to Paul Parker, who says the "complacent" Red Devils' luck ran out in their latest Premier League outing.
